cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing a deep learning-based food image recognition algorithm. 
2. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with analyzing food images captured by mobile devices. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new Convolutional Neural Network (CNN)-based approach for food image recognition. 
4. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper aims to develop computer-aided technical solutions to enhance and improve the accuracy of current measurements of dietary intake. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with deriving food information (e.g., food type and portion size) from food images effectively and efficiently.
